stock-markets</guid></item><item><title>Nuvei 同意以 27.5 亿美元的支付交易收购 Payoneer</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-15/nuvei-agrees-to-buy-payoneer-in-2-75-billion-payments-deal</link><description>Nuvei Corp. 已同意以约 27.5 亿美元收购 Payoneer Global Inc.，该交易将合并两家年处理量超过 5000 亿美元的北美支付公司。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iz4rNUG1b_TI/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Mon, 15 Jun 2026 12:51:59 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-06-15/nuvei-agrees-to-buy-payoneer-in-2-75-billion-payments-deal</guid></item></channel></rss>